Simple Modern Custom Photo Save the Date Invitation Postcard

Hot Review! Simple Modern Custom Photo Save the Date Invitation Postcard – Save The Date Invitations Simple Modern Custom Photo Save the Date Invitation Postcard ready to ship the fastest Simple Modern Custom Photo Save the Date Invitation Postcard quality productsThis simply chic photo wedding save the date postcard template features an elegant, minimalist, modern design. The front features your favorite photo with your first names and a ‘save the date’ message in white conveyed with a striking blend of two distinct fonts, with ‘the’ in a light, flowing script between the rest of the message, which is in upper case with a bold, crisp formal look.This ‘save the date’ design element can’t be altered. The default text color for the text on the back is a very dark gray that is close to black. On the back when you replace our sample info with your own, you might choose to delete text fields that you don’t need, or change the wording, as well as change font, size and color. On the back we chose an atypical order for the information, putting the ‘SAVE THE DATE’ text after the ‘FOR THE WEDDING OF’ text, which lends a path less traveled charm to it. You can alter this by changing the text in each of these text fields and entering by hand the part you want to place in the order you want to show it. The default background color on the back is set as transparent, to let the paper color simply serve as the base tone. But you can edit this by picking a particular color and change the look to suit your style. The default paper type is matte, but you can change this to semi-gloss. Customize this elegant minimalist wedding save the date postcard template with your photo and your inspiration and make it uniquely yours! Price:$1.40
